  rotatesprite x2 y2 32768 992 tilenum shade wep_pal 4100 windowx1 windowy1 windowx2 windowy2
	add y2 25
  sub x2 5
  guniqhudid 11
  rotatesprite x2 y2 40960 768 C_PISTOL_L shade wep_pal 4100 windowx1 windowy1 windowx2 windowy2
